armela-remigio/" rel="tag">Carmela Remigio</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/corrado-rovaris/" rel="tag">Corrado Rovaris</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gabriele-sagona/" rel="tag">Gabriele Sagona</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/gaetano-donizetti/" rel="tag">Gaetano Donizetti</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/i-virtuosi-italiani/" rel="tag">I Virtuosi Italiani</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/manuela-custer/" rel="tag">Manuela Custer</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/maxim-mironov/" rel="tag">Maxim Mironov</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/recensioni/" rel="tag">recensioni</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/sofia-soloviy/" rel="tag">Sofia Soloviy</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/teatro-donizetti-di-bergamo/" rel="tag">Teatro Donizetti di Bergamo</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Alessandro Talevi, Alessandro Viola, alex esposito, Anna Bolena, Carmela Remigio, Corrado Rovaris, Gabriele Sagona, Gaetano Donizetti, I Virtuosi Italiani, Manuela Custer, Maxim Mironov, Opera lirica, recensioni, Sofia Soloviy, Teatro Donizetti di Bergamo"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/f1f9fa0852d5ebce49020f737e6638fd" alt="" /> <img src="http://0.gravatar.com/avatar/f1f9fa0852d5ebce49020f737e6638fd?s=100&#038;d=mm&#038;r=g" width="100" height="100" alt="" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 photo avatar-default" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Andrea Dellabianca"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/andrea-dellabianca/">View all articles by Andrea Dellabianca</a></div></div><div class="nav-block box-shadow-2px padding-20 clearfix"> <nav class="nav-single"><h3 class="assistive-text">Post navigation</h3> <span class="nav-previous"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/12/milano-teatro-del-verme-gala-mascagni/" rel="prev"><span class="meta-nav">&larr;</span> Milano, Teatro Dal Verme: Gala Mascagni</a></span> <span class="nav-next"><a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2015/12/lopera-in-tv-a-dicembre/" rel="next">L&#8217;Opera e la Musica in Tv a dicembre <span class="meta-nav">&rarr;</span></a></span> </nav><nav class="nav-single-hidden"> <span class="nav-previous"></span> <span class="nav-next"></span><div class="clear"></div> </nav></div><div class="comments-block box-shadow-2px clearfix"><div id="comments" class="comments-area"></div></div></div></div><div id="secondary" class="widget-area span4 sb-4" role="complementary"> <aside id="search-4" class="widget widget_search clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">RICERCA</h3><form method="get" id="searchform" action="http://www.gbopera.it/"> <label for="s" class="assistive-text">Search</label> <input type="text" class="field" name="s" id="s" placeholder="Search" /> <button type="submit" class="submit btn" name="submit" id="searchsubmit"><i class="icon-search"></i></button></form> </aside><aside id="ct-relatedposts-widget-2" class="widget ct-relatedposts-widget clearfix"><h3 class="widget-title">Articoli correlati</h3><ul class="related-posts-single clearfix"><li> <a href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2016/07/martina-franca-42-festival-della-valle-ditria-la-grotta-di-trofonio/\' title=\'Martina Franca, 42 Festival della Valle d&#8217;Itria: &#8220;La grotta di Trofonio&#8221;\'><img width="70" height="70" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2016/07/1K8A1319-70x70.jpg" class="attachment-thumbnail size-thu